{"title":"外国谚语","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1981,"month":10,"day":24}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"外国谚语"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"△要想上梯子必须从底下爬起。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（德国）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"△善始是工作的一半。（德国）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"△认识到自己无知的人绝不是傻子。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（西班牙）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"△不必要的自辩等于对自己谴责。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（西班牙）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"△纵使你知道一千件事，也要请教知道一件事的人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（土耳其）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"△无知和瞎子一样。（印度）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"△一本书老是合着，不过是一块石头。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（英国）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李视岐 辑译"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":7,"page_end":7}